Completed the source-grounded prose review for the Animation feature guide. The review found the draft to be generally accurate with one significant omission: the ViewAnimationBridge property table was missing three property pairs (SizeWidth/SizeWidthBy, SizeHeight/SizeHeightBy, and CornerSquareness/CornerSquarenessBy). 

Key changes made:
1. Added missing properties to the ViewAnimationBridge table
2. Added clarification that ViewAnimationSpec supports the same properties as ViewAnimationBridge
3. Minor prose clarification for SetDuration() method name

All other content was verified against source headers including:
- Animation::New() overloads (animation.h)
- Duration literals (duration.h)
- AlphaFunction built-in values and SpringType (alpha-function.h)
- KeyFrames API (key-frames.h)
- Animation control methods, enums, and signals (animation.h)
- View::Animate() and View::NewAnimationSpec() (view.h)

The revised guide and detailed review report have been saved to animation-reviewed.md.
